{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM09_ED2_040.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x24,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "As Juris and Ayesha continued to travel<CR>together, they grew to accept that they<CR>would each always have the other's back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Juris' ambition to slay the dragon...<CR>The accomplishment of that heroic battle<CR>was only the prologue of his story."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Desiring a strong opponent...<CR>Today, their journey continues..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, according to the information, our target this time has the head of a cat, the forelegs of a bear..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "The wings of a bat, and even has a centipede for a tail."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, sounds like this target doesn't have a specific identity..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's so big, it's about as tall as that dragon we defeated a while ago."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And its savagery is even bigger than its size."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I see. It's gonna be a formidable foe. Oh, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "If it has a cat head, then it has to be vulnerable to orange peels."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You mean, not the peels themselves, but the liquid you get when you squeeze the oranges, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, yeah, that's right!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Well...our target simply looks like a cat..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And that doesn't necessarily mean that oranges will be its weakness...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat!? But, we'll never know for sure unless we try."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I agree. Then, let's go into town and buy some oranges..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hold on. We don't know when it'll pass through here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You might not get back in time if you go shopping now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's true. Hmm, this sucks..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hold on! Now that I think about it, I have some oranges with me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wow! Nanaca, you're totally prepared!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, they looked so delicious.<CR>Here, Ayesha, this one's for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Nanaca. It looks so tasty!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Here, and this one's for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...How am I supposed to use this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's so tangy and sweet and delicious! It's perfectly ripe."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Why are you eating now? You two, listen, hunting is‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x233,
            "name_id": 0x55,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "*squeeeak*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ohh."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ah shoot, it passed us by!<CR>We're going after it, Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh? But I'm still eating my orange, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Now's not the time for that...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I-I guess you're right.<CR>L-Let's go after it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Good luck, both of you. Stay safe."
        }
    ]
}